  "detailed_description": "<h1>数字豪华版</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656540/extras/0c9f6f3bfc1133f598bec8f8105b8789.avif?t=1745570674\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656540/extras_big/0c9f6f3bfc1133f598bec8f8105b8789.avif?t=1745570674 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>购买标准版的玩家后续可以选择升级成数字豪华版</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《东方：平野孤鸿》数字豪华版内含：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《东方：平野孤鸿》 游戏本体</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特殊皮肤：明镜高悬（谋士府）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特殊建筑：水月菩萨道场</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特殊谋士：引月</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特殊坐骑：万里行</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏OST原声音乐集</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏电子设定集</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※在任何游戏模式中，只要你完成了第一阶段的城镇发展目标，将自动获得特殊皮肤、特殊建筑、特殊谋士和特殊坐骑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※特殊皮肤是谋士府的专属外观。在聚宝模式或疾风模式里，你可以通过点击场景中的谋士府建筑，并点击Tips上的外观按钮来切换外观。请注意，这个特殊皮肤在桃花源模式中是无法使用的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※特殊建筑可以在营造坊的“行业”分类下的“文化”子分类中找到并建造于场景中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※特殊谋士可在谋士府中派遣上任。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※特殊坐骑需点击场景中的谋士府，然后并点击Tips右侧的【马匹】按钮。这样，你就能进入策马扬鞭模式，从中选择一个坐骑，并在场景中驰骋。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※游戏原声音乐可在原声音轨中下载</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※电子设定集可在库-BalladsOfHongye_CN-BalladsofHonyeOSTnARTBOOK中下载</p></p><br><h1>加入社区</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >老刘头喊大家来加群啦！！！！往下看！！！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方玩家QQ1群：118704538（已满） </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方玩家QQ2群：928313153（已满） </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方玩家QQ3群：727858854（已满）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方玩家QQ4群：547837946（已满）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方玩家QQ5群：971119877</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方微博：东方平野孤鸿制作组（B站同名） </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快来关注我们！获取第一手游戏动态！</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《东方：平野孤鸿》是一款休闲、轻度的“国风造景”游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与《纪元1800》、《天际线》以及《庄园领主》等诸多优秀的模拟经营游戏不同，我们并没有设计非常严谨的经营逻辑与物流机制，而是将主要精力集中在造景方面，为此，我们制作了大量细节精美的国风建筑，并在场景中还原了许多祖国的大好河山和人文景观，此外，我们还加入了一点点轻度的经营玩法，请不要担心，它们的存在仅仅是为了让你的世界看起来更加生动鲜活。王小波先生曾在万寿寺一书中写道：“一个人只拥有此生此世是不够的，他还应该拥有诗意的世界。”，说得真好，而这也正是我们的初衷，希望大家可以凭借这些元素，在平野孤鸿的世界中打造出自己心中独一无二的、充满东方韵味的古代盛世。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亲爱的朋友，欢迎你来到鸿野县。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>聚宝模式：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要通过合理经营获得更充裕的资金，以此来购买新地块扩大建造面积，在这个过程中，你可以抛开一些不必要的生存压力，安心地享受建造城市的快乐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656540/extras/8e78f92701b51085cb650bdf67d1a430.poster.avif?t=1745570674\" width=710 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656540/extras/8e78f92701b51085cb650bdf67d1a430.webm?t=1745570674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656540/extras/8e78f92701b51085cb650bdf67d1a430.mp4?t=1745570674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656540/extras/67400f7c0de91dba59008d31124643c3.poster.avif?t=1745570674\" width=710 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656540/extras/67400f7c0de91dba59008d31124643c3.webm?t=1745570674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656540/extras/67400f7c0de91dba59008d31124643c3.mp4?t=1745570674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>桃花源模式：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将前往神奇的桃花源，这里没有任何生存顾虑，你完全可以安心地享受建造城市带来的快乐。同时，你还可以移山填海、劈地开河，打造独属于你的世外盛景，山川万物、镜花水月皆由你来掌控。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656540/extras/f02be447ecea0d1a8d7d054e4f75d9b3.poster.avif?t=1745570674\" width=710 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656540/extras/f02be447ecea0d1a8d7d054e4f75d9b3.webm?t=1745570674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656540/extras/f02be447ecea0d1a8d7d054e4f75d9b3.mp4?t=1745570674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656540/extras/12f305fc51134bf5716a16f9ea4ada2d.poster.avif?t=1745570674\" width=710 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656540/extras/12f305fc51134bf5716a16f9ea4ada2d.webm?t=1745570674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656540/extras/12f305fc51134bf5716a16f9ea4ada2d.mp4?t=1745570674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方玩家1群：118704538（已满）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方玩家2群：928313153（已满）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方玩家3群：727858854</p>",
